  "subject": "Make NSD plugin jar part of sdc-backend container",
  "commit_message": "Make NSD plugin jar part of sdc-backend container\n\nThe catalog-be-plugin/etsi-nfv-nsd-csar-plugin module, responsible for\nthe NSD plugin jar, depends on the catalog-be module, but the\nsdc-backend docker image is being built on the catalog-be module.\nThe present solution:\n- adds a new module to compile the catalog-be dockers: onap/sdc-backend\nand onap/sdc-backend-init, copying the NSD plugin jar in the\nonap/sdc-backend image.\n- Improves the cleaning of the images files during the build process\n(maven clean goal).\n\nChange-Id: I64089cd4cb4ab2ca52fa759c52e40806a6a4649e\nIssue-ID: SDC-3289\nSigned-off-by: André Schmid <andre.schmid@est.tech>\n",
