        "timestamp": "2020-09-17 14:23:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-2\n\nAndré, \nI have reworked also that part, but i have done a cleanup of useless complexity in the backend be docker build in order to simplify it. \nAlso as we are talking about plugins, i would prefer to keep the existing backend image free of any plugin and have a new one based on that one (or multiples if needed) containing the plugins we want.\n\nThat new one will be referenced in OOM, so it will contain your new ETSI plugin.\n\nSorry for the concurrent work here.\n\nPlease check this PR:\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sdc/+/112824\n\nThanks, \nSeb",
        "patchset_number": 4
